headline.main: Dunk Dynasty: FGCU Tops North Florida 77-61 for NCAA Berth
headline.print_headline: Dunk Dynasty: FGCU Tops North Florida 77-61 for NCAA Berth

lead_paragraph: The "Dunk City" moniker is on their shirts, on the doors to their arena, on every press release they send out about men's basketball at Florida Gulf Coast.
